title: Department and Title of Minister) Order 2023 (S.I. No. 19 of 2023)), after
heading: 2. The 1st day of March 2023 is appointed as the day on which section 39
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of March 2023 is appointed as the day on which section 39 

of the Tailte Éireann Act 2022 (No. 50 of 2022) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

27 February, 2023. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 

Minister for Public Expenditure, National Development 
Plan Delivery and Reform. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 3rd March, 2023.
